quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,(Katonda) omusaasizi ennyo
  55,2,Yayigiriza (omuntu) Kur’ani
  55,3,Yatonda omuntu
  55,4,Yamuyizigiriza okunnyonnyola
  55,5,Enjuba n’omwezi bitambulira ku nteekateeka (eyabiweebwa)
  55,6,Ebiddo n’emiti (bivunnama nga bisinza Katonda)
  55,7,Era eggulu yalisitula era nassaawo obwenkanya
  55,8,Mube nga temusukka ebipimo (mu kutuukiriza obwenkanya)
  55,9,Era muyirizeewo ebipimo mu bwenkanya era temukendezanga minzane
  55,10,N'ensi yagiteerawo ebitonde
  55,11,Nga erimu ebibalo n’emitende egirina ebirimba
  55,12,N'ebimera ebye mpeke eziri mu bikuta n’ebimera ebya kawoowo
  55,13,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,14,Yatonda omuntu mu bumba eggumu eriringa ejjokye
  55,15,Ate naatonda amajinni mu bitawuliro by’omuliro
  55,16,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,17,"Mukama omulabirizi w’o buvanjuba bwombi, era Mukama omulabirizi w'obugwanjuba bwombi"
  55,18,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,19,Yagatta enyanja ebbiri (ez’amazzi agenjawulo aganyweka na gatanyweka) zesisinkana
  55,20,"Wakati wa zombi waliwo ekyawula, tezigenda kwetabula"
  55,21,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,22,Ate nga mu zombi mwe muva Luulu ne Marijaani (amayinja ag’omuwendo)
  55,23,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,24,Era gatambula ku lwo buyinza bwe amaato agakolwa ku lwo kutambulira ku nyanja nga galinga ensozi
  55,25,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)